# 🏢 Virtual Room Booking Platform (VRBP)  

A backend system for managing virtual room reservations efficiently and securely. Users can create, update, and cancel bookings while checking room availability in real-time. Built with **Node.js**, **Express.js**, and **Sequelize ORM** for SQL database integration.  

## 🛠 Tech Stack  
- **Node.js** - Backend runtime  
- **Express.js** - Web framework  
- **Sequelize ORM** - Database management  
- **SQL Database** (PostgreSQL/MySQL)  
- **dotenv** - Environment variable management  
- **Mocha & Chai** - Testing framework  